WEBVTT

00:00:14.270 --> 00:00:16.170
Why not let it all end?

00:00:16.510 --> 00:00:17.870
Just come over here,

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:20.370
And you can atone for your sins.

00:00:57.030 --> 00:00:57.930
Wake up.

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:00.010
You can't die.

00:01:00.140 --> 00:01:00.960
You can't...

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:22.789
The file! The file!

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:24.740
What file?

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:27.320
Just now, when I almost died,

00:01:27.450 --> 00:01:28.870
I suddenly remembered that my mentor

00:01:28.870 --> 00:01:29.810
Once sent a file

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:31.060
To the Archives.

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.130
It contained cases handled by the Chief.

00:01:35.590 --> 00:01:36.640
Some of them,

00:01:37.090 --> 00:01:37.750
I remember,

00:01:38.060 --> 00:01:39.590
Were about Nanqiang.

00:01:41.590 --> 00:01:42.390
It's said that

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:43.789
Thousands of years ago,

00:01:43.789 --> 00:01:46.759
The ancestors of the Zhang family once explored Nanqiang.

00:01:46.759 --> 00:01:48.120
Deep in the mountains and forests,

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:50.520
They found an ancient and mysterious tribe

00:01:50.870 --> 00:01:52.600
Called the ancient Wupi Tribe.

00:01:53.150 --> 00:01:54.430
According to the records,

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:56.039
They were good at using poison

00:01:56.039 --> 00:01:57.950
And manipulating evil creatures,

00:01:57.950 --> 00:01:59.410
Turning them into puppets

00:01:59.430 --> 00:02:00.430
For their own use.

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:04.190
So you're saying

00:02:05.430 --> 00:02:06.850
The poison jar mechanism just now

00:02:06.850 --> 00:02:08.850
Was set up by the ancient Wupi Tribe?

00:02:08.870 --> 00:02:09.970
What's their origin?

00:02:09.970 --> 00:02:10.699
I don't know.

00:02:11.090 --> 00:02:12.200
No one knows.

00:02:16.300 --> 00:02:17.900
What are you thinking about?

00:02:18.810 --> 00:02:19.579
I'm wondering if Zhang Haixia

00:02:19.579 --> 00:02:20.780
Also saw this file

00:02:20.780 --> 00:02:22.310
And came here because of it.

00:02:22.370 --> 00:02:23.650
His purpose is to find

00:02:23.650 --> 00:02:25.850
The Guwupi tribe deep in the mountains.

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:29.110
If there really is a Guwupi Tribe in there,

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.810
And Zhang Haixia happens to find it...

00:02:32.840 --> 00:02:35.000
What if he releases these evil creatures

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.630
All over Nanqiang?

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:37.490
Then...

00:02:38.740 --> 00:02:40.540
Then everyone will be in danger!

00:02:41.180 --> 00:02:43.060
Zhang Haixia wouldn't be that bored.

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:44.560
What good would that do him?

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:45.520
Why wouldn't he?

00:02:46.060 --> 00:02:47.120
Isn't he a lunatic?

00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:49.720
Does a lunatic need a reason to do things?

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:52.740
Zhang Haixia, what on earth do you want to do?

00:02:53.890 --> 00:02:55.690
There's no time to think about it.

00:02:55.690 --> 00:02:56.950
Since I can't find him,

00:02:58.060 --> 00:02:59.590
I'll let him find me.

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:31.370
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:04:31.650 --> 00:04:34.420
[Episode 32]

00:04:51.870 --> 00:04:53.690
There's a fragrance in this path.

00:04:53.690 --> 00:04:54.830
It seems safer.

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.470
[Cui]

00:05:02.910 --> 00:05:04.100
This is it.

00:05:05.930 --> 00:05:08.400
This is the fastest way to that place.

00:05:10.110 --> 00:05:11.160
What place?

00:05:12.760 --> 00:05:15.330
The place where we can get true freedom.

00:05:16.190 --> 00:05:17.530
Let's go now.

00:05:25.100 --> 00:05:26.550
Smells so good. Smell it.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.400
Smells good.

00:05:28.570 --> 00:05:30.840
It smells a bit like my ex.

00:05:31.180 --> 00:05:33.260
Then why don't you call out your ex

00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:34.890
And let everyone have some fun?

00:05:34.890 --> 00:05:35.810
Go to hell.

00:05:35.900 --> 00:05:38.430
There's something wrong with the fragrance.

00:05:39.250 --> 00:05:40.710
Cover your mouth and nose.

00:05:41.370 --> 00:05:42.370
Keep moving.

00:06:11.300 --> 00:06:12.360
Come on.

00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:10.620
Keep the formation.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.390
Suppressive fire.

00:07:37.950 --> 00:07:38.950
Help!

00:07:40.820 --> 00:07:42.000
Help me!

00:07:57.190 --> 00:07:59.000
Zhang Hailou is here.

00:08:17.300 --> 00:08:19.430
He's coming to kill you.

00:08:22.390 --> 00:08:23.420
Look.

00:08:24.510 --> 00:08:26.750
He abandoned you in the end.

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.750
I'll go kill him.

00:08:37.390 --> 00:08:39.080
Only when he's dead

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.460
Can you rest in peace.

00:09:08.350 --> 00:09:09.940
Then what should we do next?

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:15.220
Zhang Hailou is coming to kill me.

00:09:21.750 --> 00:09:23.080
Everyone, return immediately

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:24.360
And find Zhang Hailou.

00:09:25.990 --> 00:09:27.040
Once you spot him,

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.020
Give me a signal immediately.

00:09:29.620 --> 00:09:30.480
Keep him alive.

00:09:39.050 --> 00:09:41.510
I want to kill him myself.

00:09:41.620 --> 00:09:42.170
Yes.

00:09:43.980 --> 00:09:44.510
Let's go!

00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:45.990
Let's go!

00:10:49.370 --> 00:10:50.560
Shrimpie.

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:52.700
Didn't you say the three of us would be together?

00:10:52.700 --> 00:10:54.500
Then let's be together forever!

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.960
Aren't you curious

00:10:58.010 --> 00:10:59.770
Why I killed the Mentor?

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:05.520
Because killing others is boring.

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.000
So,

00:11:10.170 --> 00:11:12.720
I wanted to try something different.

00:13:08.700 --> 00:13:09.500
Keep chasing.

00:13:23.080 --> 00:13:24.370
So many paths?

00:13:24.910 --> 00:13:26.310
Which one should we take?

00:13:28.870 --> 00:13:30.500
Let me out!

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:35.020
Let me out!

00:13:35.150 --> 00:13:35.820
Let me...

00:13:38.270 --> 00:13:39.200
If you kill him,

00:13:39.200 --> 00:13:40.650
You won't be able to find Zhang Haixia.

00:13:40.650 --> 00:13:42.510
Do you still want to take revenge?

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:48.370
Feng Huang?

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:50.540
How... how did you find us?

00:13:52.220 --> 00:13:53.690
I heard explosions nearby

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:55.270
And thought something happened to you.

00:13:55.270 --> 00:13:57.270
I hurried over and saw this bastard.

00:13:57.410 --> 00:13:58.340
You're fine?

00:14:02.440 --> 00:14:03.130
Go out...

00:14:04.270 --> 00:14:05.910
-I want to go out. -Answer my question,

00:14:05.910 --> 00:14:07.430
And I'll spare your life for now.

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:08.300
Let me out.

00:14:08.650 --> 00:14:09.620
Let me out!

00:14:09.840 --> 00:14:10.720
I want to go out!

00:14:10.740 --> 00:14:11.720
What's wrong with him?

00:14:11.720 --> 00:14:12.390
Is he crazy?

00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:13.620
Stop pretending.

00:14:14.270 --> 00:14:15.210
I want to get out!

00:14:15.370 --> 00:14:16.260
Let me out!

00:14:16.410 --> 00:14:17.500
I want to get out.

00:14:18.430 --> 00:14:19.870
I want to get out.

00:14:20.100 --> 00:14:20.890
I want to get out.

00:14:20.890 --> 00:14:23.490
What exactly does Zhang Haixia want to do here?

00:14:24.130 --> 00:14:24.880
I want to get out.

00:14:24.880 --> 00:14:26.740
Is the ancient Wupi Tribe inside?

00:14:33.290 --> 00:14:34.090
Let me ask you,

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:36.390
Are there more black-furred snakes inside,

00:14:36.390 --> 00:14:37.360
And is the Evil God there as well?

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:39.420
Is Zhang Haixia going to control them

00:14:39.620 --> 00:14:40.880
And release them across Nanqiang,

00:14:40.880 --> 00:14:42.270
Bringing disaster to everyone?

00:14:42.270 --> 00:14:43.940
Black-furred snakes are nothing.

00:14:43.940 --> 00:14:45.330
And the Evil God is also nothing.

00:14:45.330 --> 00:14:46.930
Compared to what he's done,

00:14:47.070 --> 00:14:48.730
He's the most terrifying one!

00:14:50.740 --> 00:14:52.340
We will all be free.

00:14:52.370 --> 00:14:53.870
We will all be free!

00:14:53.890 --> 00:14:55.680
We will all be free!

00:14:55.700 --> 00:14:57.560
Let me out! Let me out!

00:14:57.590 --> 00:14:58.630
Let me out!

00:14:59.050 --> 00:14:59.940
I want to get out!

00:14:59.940 --> 00:15:00.990
I want to get out!

00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:02.740
It seems the situation now

00:15:02.740 --> 00:15:04.440
Is even more dangerous than I thought.

00:15:04.440 --> 00:15:05.740
You can go out now.

00:15:06.620 --> 00:15:07.930
I'll go in by myself.

00:15:08.360 --> 00:15:09.160
Are you crazy?

00:15:10.030 --> 00:15:10.830
I won't leave.

00:15:11.130 --> 00:15:12.660
I won't abandon my friends.

00:15:15.820 --> 00:15:17.220
Why are you looking at me?

00:15:17.610 --> 00:15:18.670
I am a member of the Zhang family.

00:15:18.670 --> 00:15:20.170
Of course, I have to complete

00:15:20.170 --> 00:15:21.770
The Zhang family's mission.

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:27.550
Although we don't know where Zhang Haixia is,

00:15:27.550 --> 00:15:28.680
Let him lead the way.

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:30.390
As long as we can get in,

00:15:30.390 --> 00:15:31.500
We will find him.

00:15:43.230 --> 00:15:44.040
This way.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:48.120
Where are Big Pot and the Snake Master?

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:49.520
Probably got separated.

00:15:50.080 --> 00:15:50.840
Time is running out.

00:15:50.840 --> 00:15:51.790
We can't wait for them.

00:15:51.790 --> 00:15:52.790
Let's leave a mark

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.750
So they can find us and regroup.

00:15:54.750 --> 00:15:56.220
I hope they are safe.

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:14.600
They're Zhang Haixia's soldiers.

00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:33.400
Their blood has been drained.

00:16:34.030 --> 00:16:35.940
How could there be such a bizarre way to die?

00:16:35.940 --> 00:16:37.630
There must be something deep in this crevice

00:16:37.630 --> 00:16:38.680
That can

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.350
Drain

00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:41.990
All the blood from a person.

00:16:53.010 --> 00:16:53.840
Keep it.

00:16:54.100 --> 00:16:55.160
It might be useful.

00:16:59.370 --> 00:16:59.920
Let's go.

00:17:02.170 --> 00:17:02.770
Let's go.

00:17:04.380 --> 00:17:04.750
Let's go.

00:17:04.750 --> 00:17:05.089
No!

00:17:05.530 --> 00:17:06.200
No!

00:17:06.200 --> 00:17:06.829
Let's go!

00:17:07.829 --> 00:17:09.069
No! Let me out!

00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:10.740
Behave yourself!

00:17:11.790 --> 00:17:12.660
Let me out!

00:17:21.970 --> 00:17:27.230
[Wupi Ancient City]

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:26.849
This should be the entrance to the Wupi Ancient City.

00:17:26.849 --> 00:17:28.940
Zhang Haixia and the dead soldiers

00:17:29.270 --> 00:17:30.470
Should all be inside.

00:17:31.670 --> 00:17:32.740
I don't want to go back!

00:17:32.740 --> 00:17:33.310
No!

00:17:33.310 --> 00:17:34.070
Come here!

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:34.720
No!

00:17:35.440 --> 00:17:35.790
Go!

00:17:35.790 --> 00:17:36.790
Behave yourself!

00:17:40.510 --> 00:17:41.270
No!

00:17:41.530 --> 00:17:42.480
No!

00:17:42.480 --> 00:17:43.480
Behave yourself!

00:17:44.140 --> 00:17:45.010
No!

00:17:45.510 --> 00:17:46.910
He wants to kill himself.

00:17:47.310 --> 00:17:49.240
It won't be that easy for him to die.

00:17:49.420 --> 00:17:49.850
Go!

00:17:49.850 --> 00:17:50.590
No!

00:17:50.890 --> 00:17:51.220
Go!

00:17:51.220 --> 00:17:51.810
Go!

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:53.570
Hurry up!

00:17:54.090 --> 00:17:54.830
No!

00:17:55.350 --> 00:17:55.830
Go!

00:17:56.770 --> 00:17:57.590
No!

00:18:29.180 --> 00:18:29.850
Which way?

00:19:05.460 --> 00:19:08.060
These are the narrative murals of the ancient Wupi people.

00:19:08.060 --> 00:19:10.860
It looks like they were fighting wars everywhere.

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:29.910
These are black-furred snakes?

00:19:30.960 --> 00:19:32.410
So this ancient tribe

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:34.370
Had been raising these snakes.

00:19:34.420 --> 00:19:35.880
They even used them in wars

00:19:36.220 --> 00:19:39.020
To seize the territories of other ancient tribes.

00:19:41.070 --> 00:19:42.130
There's more here.

00:19:55.070 --> 00:19:56.810
This painting probably shows that

00:19:56.810 --> 00:19:58.270
The ancient Wupi people made

00:19:58.270 --> 00:19:59.730
A bizarre Evil God statue.

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:03.220
After these little black-furred snakes went into hibernation,

00:20:03.220 --> 00:20:05.070
They would put them

00:20:05.090 --> 00:20:06.490
Into the Evil God statue.

00:20:07.590 --> 00:20:09.460
If an external force caused a shock

00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:10.770
And woke the snakes up,

00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:13.960
They would break through the statue

00:20:13.960 --> 00:20:15.020
And move together.

00:20:16.570 --> 00:20:17.640
It would look

00:20:17.850 --> 00:20:19.580
Like the god statue came alive.

00:20:20.350 --> 00:20:22.070
But the most terrifying part is

00:20:22.070 --> 00:20:23.700
That these little black-furred snakes

00:20:23.700 --> 00:20:24.960
Can mimic human speech

00:20:25.140 --> 00:20:26.160
Like parrots.

00:20:27.220 --> 00:20:30.080
By controlling these little black-furred snakes,

00:20:30.160 --> 00:20:32.090
They could make the Evil God statue

00:20:32.290 --> 00:20:33.220
Appear to

00:20:33.830 --> 00:20:35.000
Move and speak.

00:20:39.000 --> 00:20:40.460
There's another one here.

00:20:54.810 --> 00:20:56.110
Other ancient tribes

00:20:56.220 --> 00:20:57.820
All thought it was a true god.

00:20:57.960 --> 00:21:00.830
So they worshipped and made offerings to the Evil God.

00:21:00.830 --> 00:21:02.030
Little did they know,

00:21:02.290 --> 00:21:04.000
This was all a conspiracy of the ancient Wupi people.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:05.200
By creating a fake god

00:21:05.810 --> 00:21:07.780
And brainwashing others,

00:21:08.250 --> 00:21:09.220
They could control the surrounding tribes

00:21:09.220 --> 00:21:11.080
Without losing a single soldier.

00:21:12.660 --> 00:21:14.590
Sure enough, the Evil God is a hoax.

00:21:15.460 --> 00:21:17.860
These ancient Wupi people were very smart.

00:21:18.140 --> 00:21:20.270
Let's see if there are any other clues.

00:21:22.070 --> 00:21:23.030
The more we know,

00:21:23.030 --> 00:21:25.960
The better we'll understand what Zhang Haixia wants to do.

00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:28.290
Then we can figure out how to deal with him.

00:23:16.180 --> 00:23:17.110
What's going on?

00:23:17.350 --> 00:23:18.330
Look at this rat.

00:23:18.850 --> 00:23:20.250
Its blood was sucked dry.

00:23:21.070 --> 00:23:22.530
It only took 1 or 2 seconds.

00:23:23.310 --> 00:23:24.770
I have a feeling that

00:23:25.740 --> 00:23:27.800
There is something else around here.

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:34.250
Then where

00:23:34.440 --> 00:23:35.570
Should we go next?

00:23:38.070 --> 00:23:38.530
Here.

00:24:03.740 --> 00:24:05.200
There's another one here?

00:24:24.330 --> 00:24:25.140
As expected,

00:24:25.240 --> 00:24:26.980
The big Evil God we fought earlier

00:24:26.980 --> 00:24:29.380
Was the mother of the black-furred snakes.

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:30.700
The reason why the large and small Evil God statues

00:24:30.700 --> 00:24:32.700
Could make the exact same movements

00:24:33.070 --> 00:24:36.010
Is that these black-furred snakes can communicate with each other

00:24:36.010 --> 00:24:37.270
And mimic one another.

00:24:41.550 --> 00:24:42.610
The actions and behaviors of these 2 things

00:24:42.610 --> 00:24:43.470
Are identical.

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:45.600
They can control each other.

00:24:46.980 --> 00:24:48.380
The case from 10 years ago

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:50.080
Has been solved here.

00:24:50.410 --> 00:24:51.340
Come take a look.

00:25:00.330 --> 00:25:01.790
These ancient Wupi people

00:25:02.220 --> 00:25:03.310
Gave their captured prisoners of war

00:25:03.310 --> 00:25:05.520
To a strange stone.

00:25:06.030 --> 00:25:08.050
And then this prisoner became...

00:25:11.240 --> 00:25:13.100
What is this? I can't see clearly.

00:25:13.770 --> 00:25:15.300
Why can't I scrape this off?

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:18.610
Just now,

00:25:19.740 --> 00:25:21.340
Were these black spots here?

00:25:22.290 --> 00:25:23.690
I remember they weren't.

00:25:26.510 --> 00:25:27.090
Right.

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:29.070
They weren't here just now.

00:25:29.070 --> 00:25:31.000
How could they appear so suddenly?

00:25:31.290 --> 00:25:33.290
These black spots don't look right.

00:25:33.300 --> 00:25:34.630
He must know something.

00:25:40.180 --> 00:25:41.710
Do you know something?

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:45.050
What are you looking at?

00:25:49.180 --> 00:25:49.770
Tell me

00:25:50.860 --> 00:25:52.190
What you are looking at.

00:25:52.830 --> 00:25:54.590
Or I'll gouge your eyes out.

00:25:58.380 --> 00:25:59.090
Nothing.

00:26:00.240 --> 00:26:01.170
My neck is stiff.

00:26:01.740 --> 00:26:02.740
I'm taking a rest.

00:26:03.460 --> 00:26:04.320
Zhang Hailou.

00:26:04.550 --> 00:26:05.220
Look.

00:26:21.960 --> 00:26:24.700
Is the wall... growing hair?

00:26:25.530 --> 00:26:26.740
What is this?

00:26:27.240 --> 00:26:27.900
Don't move.

00:26:28.850 --> 00:26:29.980
Keep your head down.

00:26:30.290 --> 00:26:30.770
What?

00:26:30.920 --> 00:26:32.050
Keep your head down.

00:26:32.430 --> 00:26:33.290
Whatever Li Pinrui does,

00:26:33.290 --> 00:26:34.190
You do the same.

00:26:46.060 --> 00:26:47.130
What is that?

00:26:48.660 --> 00:26:49.610
What is that?

00:26:50.160 --> 00:26:51.220
If you want to know,

00:26:51.610 --> 00:26:52.680
Look up.

00:27:07.790 --> 00:27:08.720
My God.

00:27:33.810 --> 00:27:34.740
What is that?

00:28:15.900 --> 00:28:17.100
They can't be killed!

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:27.740
Zhang Qianjun!

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:28.890
The explosives!

00:28:55.550 --> 00:28:56.530
Little Taoist.

00:28:57.750 --> 00:28:58.480
Feng Huang.

00:29:00.720 --> 00:29:01.790
Little Taoist.

00:29:03.250 --> 00:29:04.240
Are you still alive?

00:29:04.240 --> 00:29:05.030
I'm fine.

00:29:06.530 --> 00:29:07.220
My leg...

00:29:07.250 --> 00:29:08.780
Feng Huang's leg is pinned!

00:29:11.150 --> 00:29:12.950
Don't lift the stone right away.

00:29:13.000 --> 00:29:14.460
Her blood flow is blocked.

00:29:14.660 --> 00:29:15.950
If you move it too fast,

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:17.740
Her leg

00:29:18.420 --> 00:29:19.620
Might get paralyzed.

00:29:20.400 --> 00:29:21.790
Then... then what should we do?

00:29:21.790 --> 00:29:22.720
Do something!

00:29:23.830 --> 00:29:24.830
What should we do?

00:29:24.940 --> 00:29:25.530
What should we do?

00:29:25.530 --> 00:29:26.250
It hurts.

00:29:26.660 --> 00:29:27.330
I'll be gentle.

00:29:27.330 --> 00:29:28.190
I'll be gentle.

00:29:54.350 --> 00:29:56.270
Zhang Hailou.

00:29:57.500 --> 00:29:59.070
Since we were kids,

00:29:59.550 --> 00:30:00.700
You've always had the ability

00:30:00.700 --> 00:30:02.330
To mess things up.

00:30:05.740 --> 00:30:07.030
In this field,

00:30:07.050 --> 00:30:09.140
You're very gifted.

00:31:46.140 --> 00:31:46.940
Zhang Hailou?

00:31:48.160 --> 00:31:49.010
Zhang Hailou?

00:31:50.810 --> 00:31:51.340
Zhang...

00:31:57.880 --> 00:31:58.680
Zhang Hailou?

00:32:16.180 --> 00:32:17.350
You... you're dead?

00:32:27.550 --> 00:32:29.430
I'm finally free.

00:32:36.290 --> 00:32:37.110
Let's go.

00:33:19.480 --> 00:33:20.770
This is the place.

00:33:25.740 --> 00:33:26.440
Blow it up!

00:33:26.550 --> 00:33:26.880
Yes!

00:33:26.880 --> 00:33:27.310
Yes!

00:33:39.960 --> 00:33:41.640
Keep blowing it up!

00:33:44.010 --> 00:33:44.870
No need to look.

00:33:46.350 --> 00:33:47.410
He's already dead.

00:33:47.850 --> 00:33:49.530
He was just talking.

00:33:51.350 --> 00:33:53.040
How could he be dead now?

00:33:56.160 --> 00:33:57.420
It's Zhang Haixia.

00:34:01.090 --> 00:34:02.220
Where are you going?

00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:03.440
I'm going to kill him!

00:34:03.610 --> 00:34:06.010
Killing Zhang Haixia won't bring him back.

00:34:07.640 --> 00:34:08.400
Mr. Zhang!

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:09.820
Mr. Zhang!

00:34:16.610 --> 00:34:18.210
Mr. Zhang can still be saved.

00:34:19.110 --> 00:34:20.010
He's dead.

00:34:20.350 --> 00:34:21.409
How can he be saved?

00:34:21.590 --> 00:34:23.320
Hurry up and pull out the knife.

00:34:25.840 --> 00:34:26.650
Hurry!

00:34:30.340 --> 00:34:30.960
Hold it.

00:34:38.940 --> 00:34:40.199
What did you put on him?

00:34:40.710 --> 00:34:41.610
This is snake medicine.

00:34:41.610 --> 00:34:42.719
It can stop the bleeding.

00:34:42.719 --> 00:34:44.250
He was stabbed in the heart.

00:34:44.340 --> 00:34:45.429
Even God himself

00:34:45.650 --> 00:34:46.980
Couldn't save his life.

00:34:47.050 --> 00:34:47.780
Don't worry.

00:34:50.110 --> 00:34:51.620
God is here.

00:34:52.710 --> 00:34:53.520
Zhang Hailou?

00:34:56.480 --> 00:34:57.280
Zhang Hailou?

00:34:57.530 --> 00:34:58.860
You... you're alright?

00:34:59.170 --> 00:35:01.420
Were you holding your breath to play dead?

00:35:01.420 --> 00:35:02.280
It couldn't be.

00:35:02.570 --> 00:35:04.630
The knife went right into your heart.

00:35:05.460 --> 00:35:06.920
How did you manage to do it?

00:35:07.000 --> 00:35:09.010
Most orphans adopted by the Archives

00:35:09.010 --> 00:35:10.880
Are not like normal people.

00:35:11.090 --> 00:35:12.460
My heart is on the right.

00:35:13.530 --> 00:35:15.530
And I lured the Snake Master here in advance.

00:35:15.530 --> 00:35:16.680
My mentor told me

00:35:16.710 --> 00:35:17.840
That your snake medicine is very effective

00:35:17.840 --> 00:35:19.440
And stops bleeding quickly.

00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:21.000
You knew

00:35:21.150 --> 00:35:22.550
He would come to kill you?

00:35:24.020 --> 00:35:24.660
Wait.

00:35:25.280 --> 00:35:28.420
Doesn't Zhang Haixia know your heart is on the right?

00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:30.550
He does.

00:35:32.290 --> 00:35:34.360
So that wasn't Zhang Haixia just now.

00:35:35.070 --> 00:35:36.340
It was someone else.

00:35:37.070 --> 00:35:39.670
There are 2 people inside Zhang Haixia's body.

00:35:48.780 --> 00:35:50.510
And the moment he saw my mentor—

00:35:50.920 --> 00:35:52.060
Only Shrimpie

00:35:52.530 --> 00:35:54.330
Would have that look in his eyes.

00:35:54.920 --> 00:35:55.340
And then?

00:35:55.340 --> 00:35:57.200
Mr. Zhang needs to take a rest now.

00:35:58.820 --> 00:36:00.020
By the way, Mr. Zhang.

00:36:02.820 --> 00:36:04.650
We found this on your mentor.

00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:08.480
This snake is very special.

00:36:08.480 --> 00:36:09.760
It can store memories.

00:36:10.000 --> 00:36:10.940
Once bitten by it,

00:36:10.940 --> 00:36:12.300
You can see what it saw.

00:36:12.630 --> 00:36:13.920
It will tell you everything

00:36:13.920 --> 00:36:15.030
You want to know.

00:36:15.650 --> 00:36:16.510
Snake charmer.

00:36:17.150 --> 00:36:18.690
No matter how powerful your snake is,

00:36:18.690 --> 00:36:20.160
It's no match for guns.

00:36:20.400 --> 00:36:21.880
Have it find a way to escape quickly.

00:36:21.880 --> 00:36:22.300
Okay.

00:36:22.300 --> 00:36:22.900
Take this.

00:36:23.940 --> 00:36:24.980
Escape now.

00:36:31.090 --> 00:36:33.040
Why does your snake even bite you?

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:34.420
Help...

00:36:52.590 --> 00:36:53.170
What?

00:36:54.510 --> 00:36:55.150
This snake

00:36:56.170 --> 00:36:58.260
Is a relic of Mr. Zhang's mentor.

00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:05.650
Zhang Hailou!

00:37:05.650 --> 00:37:06.900
Don't worry, don't worry!

00:37:06.900 --> 00:37:07.500
He's fine.

00:37:19.340 --> 00:37:20.170
Zhang Hailou.

00:37:19.670 --> 00:37:23.070
[Mo Yungao's Base in Xiaojiang]

00:37:21.690 --> 00:37:24.090
The pitcher plant plan has been shattered.

00:37:24.550 --> 00:37:26.090
The Southern Archives' annihilation

00:37:26.090 --> 00:37:27.350
Has also been avenged.

00:37:27.500 --> 00:37:29.830
Now I must fulfill my promise to the Mentor

00:37:29.860 --> 00:37:30.820
And carry out

00:37:30.820 --> 00:37:32.820
A highly dangerous secret mission.

00:37:33.690 --> 00:37:35.610
This mission is of great importance.

00:37:35.610 --> 00:37:37.010
It will last for 30 years

00:37:37.760 --> 00:37:39.820
And is the top secret of the Archives.

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:43.320
Unfortunately, your current rank is too low

00:37:43.320 --> 00:37:45.580
To shoulder this heavy responsibility.

00:37:45.980 --> 00:37:47.150
Therefore, we cannot

00:37:47.150 --> 00:37:48.750
Go together on this mission.

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:51.340
If you want to find me,

00:37:51.980 --> 00:37:53.580
You need to work much harder.

00:37:56.380 --> 00:37:57.580
Only then can we meet.

00:37:58.610 --> 00:37:59.660
Meanwhile,

00:38:01.150 --> 00:38:03.150
Please take good care of our mentor.

00:38:03.920 --> 00:38:05.040
Do not be careless.

00:38:06.380 --> 00:38:07.420
In 30 years,

00:38:07.710 --> 00:38:09.820
[To Zhang Hailou]

00:38:08.420 --> 00:38:10.550
We will surely meet again in Xiacheng.

00:38:11.630 --> 00:38:12.940
Take care and be well.

00:38:14.440 --> 00:38:15.900
Sincerely, Zhang Haixia.

00:39:56.990 --> 00:39:58.650
What exactly do you want to do?

00:39:58.670 --> 00:39:59.800
Tell me!

00:40:39.870 --> 00:40:41.130
Black-furred snakes.

00:41:21.580 --> 00:41:24.460
[Research Report: Black-Furred Snake]

00:41:26.760 --> 00:41:27.160
[Black-furred snakea are enormous in size and extremely aggressive]

00:41:27.180 --> 00:41:28.290
[Visual and Sense]

00:41:28.320 --> 00:41:29.610
[Nerve System and Toxin]

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:31.900
They're researching

00:41:31.900 --> 00:41:34.960
The habits and pheromones of the black-furred snakes?

00:41:42.560 --> 00:41:47.500
[Deployment of Twilight Grass Drop Points and Plantations]

00:41:49.400 --> 00:41:51.590
Mo Yungao has another Twilight Grass

00:41:50.330 --> 00:41:52.580
[Drop Point 1] [Drop Point 2] [Drop Point 3]

00:41:51.650 --> 00:41:52.690
Plantation?

00:41:52.810 --> 00:41:53.370
[Drop Point 4]

00:41:52.960 --> 00:41:54.840
It's at the border of Bailejing and the Bone-Washing Cave.

00:41:53.480 --> 00:41:54.730
[Border of Bailejing and the Bone-Washing Cave]

00:41:58.030 --> 00:41:59.340
This isn't over yet.

00:42:26.070 --> 00:42:27.050
Go back to here.

00:42:28.920 --> 00:42:30.720
I need to go back to this place.

00:42:30.740 --> 00:42:31.630
What's in here?

00:42:33.650 --> 00:42:36.090
This is where it all began.

00:42:38.730 --> 00:42:40.610
Don't even think about using me again.

00:42:40.610 --> 00:42:42.670
Then I'll kill the people around you.

00:42:45.500 --> 00:42:46.860
You can try.

00:42:48.360 --> 00:42:49.530
You can't speak,

00:42:50.340 --> 00:42:51.480
Nor can you write.

00:42:52.630 --> 00:42:54.960
You can't even die.

00:42:55.190 --> 00:42:56.960
You can control my body.

00:42:58.330 --> 00:43:00.260
But you can't control my mind.

00:43:00.510 --> 00:43:01.820
I'll do everything I can

00:43:01.820 --> 00:43:02.940
To destroy you.

00:43:05.630 --> 00:43:07.430
Otherwise, I'm just a criminal.

00:43:09.050 --> 00:43:10.590
We are one.

00:43:13.380 --> 00:43:15.010
We're accomplices.

00:43:32.940 --> 00:43:33.570
Hello.

00:43:36.360 --> 00:43:37.530
Mo Yungao, right?

00:43:39.590 --> 00:43:40.900
Your men are all dead.

00:43:41.500 --> 00:43:42.480
Who are you?

00:43:44.320 --> 00:43:47.460
Agent Zhang Haixia of the Southern Archives.

